{"tid":2439974,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"緬甸警察現辭職潮　反軍政府與民同行","createTime":"2021-03-09T15:22:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T15:33:54.000Z","uid":261647,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fab8f3ea67081dd3554ab8b62b2974543a0f98df","tid":2439974,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T15:22:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/WhatsNewsMedia/posts/224447662748027\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FWhatsNewsMedia%2Fposts%2F224447662748027&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1Mhy0zKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=6ad1df40\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/WhatsNewsMedia/posts/224447662748027</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：和你報WhatsNewsMedia<br />\n<br />\n[緬甸警察現辭職潮<br />\n反軍政府與民同行]<br />\n<br />\n緬甸反軍政府示威持續，軍政府近日屢次血腥鎮壓，採取空陸兩路襲擊市民如同戰爭，引起全球嘩然。<br />\n<br />\n緬甸警察陸續辭職表示支持市民，並且身體力行加入反軍政府示威，與民同行。據了解，現時辭職人數超過600人。社交平台上亦出現不少警察舉起「三指禮」，以示對政權的表態。<br />\n<br />\n一名少校於社交平台發文表示不希望服役與軍事政權之下，現參與公民抗命運動，對反軍政府運動的年輕抗爭者表示敬意。<br />\n<br />\n警察，對於不少人來說是一份稱為「鐵飯碗」的工作，豐厚的薪金和福利吸引不少求職者青睞。但警察屬於公務員的一群，作為人民公僕理應以服務人民為先。倘若接受指令需要與民為敵，執行的任務與職責背道而馳，如何選擇則能取決於其入職的理由是為名利或是使命。<br />\n<br />\n#緬甸 #反軍政府 #CDM #警察 #辭職 #與民同行"},{"pid":"0caa86ded9669ce28458a516abd3986b8d323b9d","tid":2439974,"uid":261647,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T15:23:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EgFowoZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEgFowoZ.jpg&h=acffbe36&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4ef186f04be388ed1ec394ad39fc083dfa3fd04f","tid":2439974,"uid":87690,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T15:28:09.000Z","msg":"左下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0534f12652956a2fd5410b09cab630dd552b9a0","tid":2439974,"uid":238370,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T15:29:42.000Z","msg":"反觀猩講啲狗隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9471c4664a3ac03fbffe29589337b900c5e75f2","tid":2439974,"uid":378793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0534f12652956a2fd5410b09cab630dd552b9a0","tid":2439974,"uid":238370,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T15:29:42.000Z","msg":"反觀猩講啲狗隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T15:33:54.000Z","msg":"有一隻痴下文宣"}]}